Class ProximityEntry

java.lang.Object
  com.m87.sdk.ProximityEntry

public class ProximityEntry
extends java.lang.Object

Object representing a proximate device

The SDK will pass an ProximityEntry object in events when a proximate device has a change in status.

See Also:
